{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create a premium Shopify Online Store 2.0 section called "Recent Deliveries".
    
    The design should be modern, compact, clean and mobile-first.
    
    Use a Red, White and Black colour scheme.
    
    The layout should feel like a premium service company, not an ecommerce product grid.
    
    ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
