    Load all jobs dynamically from the page metafield:
    
    custom.recent_jobs
    
    This metafield is a List of Recent Job metaobject references.
    
    Loop through:
    
    page.metafields.custom.recent_jobs.value
    
    Never use manual blocks.
    
    Never hardcode any job content.
    
    If there are no Recent Jobs assigned to the page, hide the entire section.
    
    ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
    RECENT JOB METAOBJECT FIELDS
